title: In The Parks With Neff | Neff Skate Team
description:
http://www.neffheadwear.com/skate
The Neff Skate Team gets together for a little fun at Windells Summer camp for this edition of "In The Parks With Neff." Watch team members Silas Baxter-Neal, Aaron Homoki, Leo Romero, Nick Merlino, Matt Bennet, and Derrick Wilson throw down at the park. From steezy tail slides to big gap transfers, these talented skaters rip up the park. Enjoy.
